#. (itstool) path: sect2/title
#: C/index.docbook:461
msgid "XDMCP"
msgstr "XDMCP"

#. (itstool) path: sect2/para
#: C/index.docbook:470
msgid ""
"The GDM daemon can be configured to listen for and manage X Display Manage Protocol (XDMCP) requests from remote displays. By default "
